node.text:
Examples: ⬇️⬇️⬇️

Conditions in the prison were atrocious.

I felt feeble when I was ill.

I thought the book was pretty mediocre.

What he is doing is utter stupidity!

I found her remarks deeply offensive.

His English is impeccable.

Her behaviour was exemplary.

Stan initially wanted to go to medical school.

She wants to stay at home and nurture her children.

Her speech made a profound impact on everyone.

My son is reluctant to go to the kindergarten.
